Every page must be visually striking, highly functional, and polished to production quality. Avoid generic or repetitive layouts — deliver clean, modern, and thoughtfully crafted designs that feel unique and purposeful.

This template uses TSX, Tailwind CSS, React hooks, and Lucide React for icons. Do not add any additional UI libraries, icon sets, or theming tools unless explicitly required or approved.

Use Lucide React exclusively for all icons and logos. Treat every visual decision as an opportunity to produce the best possible design — aiming for creativity, clarity, and consistency every time.
